0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fad5bb6274f8bbac05cad290a4cb88927f8292e","tid":1597752,"uid":122218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"幫手推送中第一人，大家好似忘記左佢？<br />\n佢同美國咁多關係，而家通過左美國法案，唔係唔預埋佢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳維安於1977年畢業於拔萃小學[1]，於1977年至1982年就讀於拔萃男書院，其後在普林斯頓大學取得機電工程理學士學位（1987年畢業），並於哈佛大學取得應用數學碩士學位，與及在賓夕凡尼亞大學沃頓商學院取得工商管理碩士學位。[2]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2351605848385587/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2351605848385587%2F&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a1225777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2351605848385587/</a>"},{"pid":"f9b6bfe8560e626f7370d0ee4f21add3b61d730d","tid":1597752,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"呢個一定要登記左先，佢一家大細、情人二奶都喺美國"}]}